							<span class="benefit-tag">Conteúdo Corporativo</span>
						</div>
					</div> -->

					<!-- <div class="timeline-section">
						<div class="timeline-item">
							<div class="timeline-icon">
								<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
									<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
									<polyline points="12,6 12,12 16,14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div class="timeline-content">
								<strong>Início das gravações:</strong>
								<span>Junho de 2025</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div> -->

					<div class="cta-section">
						<a href="#contato" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg cta-button">
							<span>Quero Gravar Meu Conteúdo</span>
							<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="why-choose">
			<h3>Por que gravar no Studio P7 Criativo?</h3>
			<div class="reasons-grid">
				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M21 10C21 17 12 23 12 23S3 17 3 10C3 5.02944 7.02944 1 12 1C16.9706 1 21 5.02944 21 10Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
							<circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Localização Privilegiada</h4>
					<p>No centro de BH, fácil acesso e ambiente inspirador no 24º andar</p>
				</div>
				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M16 21V19C16 17.9391 15.5786 16.9217 14.8284 16.1716C14.0783 15.4214 13.0609 15 12 15H5C3.93913 15 2.92172 15.4214 2.17157 16.1716C1.42143 16.9217 1 17.9391 1 19V21M12.5 7.5C12.5 9.98528 10.4853 12 8 12C5.51472 12 3.5 9.98528 3.5 7.5C3.5 5.01472 5.51472 3 8 3C10.4853 3 12.5 5.01472 12.5 7.5ZM20 8V14M23 11H17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							<circle cx="20" cy="11" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Parceria de Excelência</h4>
					<p>4Nexus, uma das principais produtoras de conteúdo do país</p>
				</div>
				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
							<path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9L17 14L18.18 21L12 17.77L5.82 21L7 14L2 9L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Ambiente Moderno</h4>
					<p>Profissional e inspirador para seu melhor conteúdo</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.pricing {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D2D2D 0%, #1A1A1A 100%);
		color: white;
	}

	.pricing-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		color: white;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	}

	.section-subtitle.centered {
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.promo-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		animation: pulse 2s infinite;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
	}

	.badge-icon {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.pricing-container {
		display: block;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 5rem;
	}

	.pricing-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border-radius: 2rem;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.2);
		position: relative;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.pricing-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 6px;
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
	}

	.pricing-header-card {
		/* background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); */
		padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.price-badge {
		background: var(--secondary-yellow);
		color: var(--black);
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.price {
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.currency {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--primary-coral);
	}

	.amount {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.period {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--primary-coral);
	}

	.price-subtitle {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.pricing-content {
		padding: 2.5rem;
	}

	.features-section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.features-section h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.features-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.1);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.2);
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.feature-item:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.15);
		transform: translateX(4px);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		flex-shrink: 0;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.feature-text {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.25rem;
	}

	.feature-text strong {
		color: white;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-text span {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.benefits-section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.benefits-section h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.benefits-tags {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.benefit-tag {
		background: var(--primary-coral);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.timeline-section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		background: rgba(255, 184, 61, 0.15);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 184, 61, 0.3);
	}

	.timeline-icon {
		color: var(--primary-orange);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.25rem;
	}

	.timeline-content strong {
		color: white;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.timeline-content span {
		color: var(--primary-orange);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-button {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.cta-subtitle {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.pricing-sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.value-highlight {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.2);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.value-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.value-icon {
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.value-header h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.value-stats {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.value-stat {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.1);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.2);
	}

	.value-stat.highlight {
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
		color: white;
	}

	.value-stat .stat-number {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
		display: block;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.value-stat.highlight .stat-number {
		color: white;
	}

	.value-stat .stat-label {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
	}

	.value-stat.highlight .stat-label {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.guarantee-card {
		background: var(--gradient-primary);
		color: white;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.guarantee-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -50%;
		right: -50%;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.guarantee-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.guarantee-icon {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.guarantee-header h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.guarantee-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.guarantee-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.guarantee-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.guarantee-list li {
		padding: 0.25rem 0;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
	}

	.guarantee-list li::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0.5rem;
		width: 6px;
		height: 6px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.why-choose {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.why-choose h3 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.reasons-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.reason-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 90, 61, 0.2);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.reason-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.reason-icon {
		color: var(--primary-coral);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.reason-card h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.reason-card p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.pricing-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.pricing-header-card {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.pricing-content {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.amount {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.features-list {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.feature-item {
			padding: 0.75rem;
		}

		.value-highlight,
		.guarantee-card {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.reasons-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.why-choose h3 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.reason-card {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>